What is a Parametric Trigger?
A parametric trigger is an objective, pre-defined threshold tied to real-world data. When the threshold is crossed, a claim is automatically initiated — no subjective assessment, no claim officer, no paperwork. The data source decides, not a person.
This eliminates the #1 pain point in traditional insurance: disputed claims.

